# 🎫 Help Desk Ticket

## Issue

Employee cannot open a backup file received from another office.

File Name

backup.tar.gz

### Investigation

Verified the file extension.

Identified that the file was archived and compressed.

### Resolution

Step 1

```bash
gunzip backup.tar.gz
```

Step 2

```bash
tar -xvf backup.tar
```

Or

```bash
tar -xzvf backup.tar.gz
```

Issue resolved successfully.

